{"synckey":1612819012,"updated":[{"bookId":"920788","bookmarkId":"920788_9_27833-27946","chapterUid":9,"markText":"制药、消费电子、酒类、零售、日用化工、汽车等行业股票一般多为独立型。一般地，房地产、银行、电力、能源、交通运输、金属等行业的股票一般多为大盘型。一般地，重型机械、证券、通信、软件、餐饮旅游、纺织服装等行业的股票一般多为多元型。","range":"29267-29380","createTime":1584954109,"type":1},{"bookId":"920788","bookmarkId":"920788_9_2039-2065","chapterUid":9,"markText":"选股应重点考虑公司业务的竞争力、成长性、长期稳定性。","range":"2115-2141","createTime":1584922390,"type":1},{"bookId":"920788","bookmarkId":"920788_8_9951-9995","chapterUid":8,"markText":"乌龟精神：乌龟的忍耐、谨慎与长寿三种特质尽显价值投资的复利本色。复利增值要学习乌龟精神。","range":"10351-10395","createTime":1584888034,"type":1},{"bookId":"920788","bookmarkId":"920788_8_9819-9852","chapterUid":8,"markText":"选股：稳定、高增长是根本标准。抗通胀、垄断性企业是理想的投资对象。","range":"9819-9852","createTime":1584888017,"type":1},{"bookId":"920788","bookmarkId":"920788_8_9621-9650","chapterUid":8,"markText":"复利增值考验人性弱点：浪费与冒险、贪婪与妒忌、急躁与恐惧。","range":"9621-9650","createTime":1584887987,"type":1},{"bookId":"920788","bookmarkId":"920788_8_9570-9590","chapterUid":8,"markText":"复利增值彰显人性优点：勤俭、智勇与耐心。","range":"9570-9590","createTime":1584887976,"type":1},{"bookId":"920788","bookmarkId":"920788_8_9520-9539","chapterUid":8,"markText":"复利增值三要素：本金、收益率与投资期。","range":"9920-9939","createTime":1584887973,"type":1},{"bookId":"920788","bookmarkId":"920788_7_18620-18646","chapterUid":7,"markText":"“回报高”的要求是：本金安全是底线，定好目标不贪婪。","range":"18620-18646","createTime":1584887879,"type":1},{"bookId":"920788","bookmarkId":"920788_7_18562-18588","chapterUid":7,"markText":"“分析好”的要求是：定性定量都要有，简单稳定最可靠。","range":"18562-18588","createTime":1584887875,"type":1},{"bookId":"920788","bookmarkId":"920788_7_18472-18531","chapterUid":7,"markText":"价值投资四项基本原则是：精选个股原则、安全边际原则、组合投资原则、长期投资原则。四项基本原则有助于确保投资的本金安全。","range":"19347-19406","createTime":1584887860,"type":1},{"bookId":"920788","bookmarkId":"920788_7_744-830","chapterUid":7,"markText":"安全边际类似于商品折扣，比值越低越好。安全边际要求物超所值（即“便宜”），故投资本质是“通过全面分析买到真正便宜货”。巴菲特一生践行安全边际，是全球最擅长“买便宜货”的人。","range":"744-830","createTime":1584887407,"type":1},{"bookId":"920788","bookmarkId":"920788_6_31988-32101","chapterUid":6,"markText":"针对股市五个基本特性，投资者应该具备正确心态：精心（全面分析，精选好股）、宽容心（容忍短期随机涨跌）、爱心（股票低估时买入，股票高估时卖出）、小心（防止大跌）与耐心（等待大涨）、自信心（坚持正确思考）与孤独心（坚持独立思考）。","range":"31988-32101","createTime":1584887283,"type":1}],"removed":[],"chapters":[{"title":"第2章　认识投资","chapterUid":7,"chapterIdx":7},{"title":"第3章　复利威力","chapterUid":8,"chapterIdx":8},{"title":"第1章　透视股市","chapterUid":6,"chapterIdx":6},{"title":"第4章　选股要诀","chapterUid":9,"chapterIdx":9}],"book":{"bookId":"920788","version":1787629443,"format":"epub","soldout":0,"bookStatus":1,"cover":"https://wfqqreader-1252317822.image.myqcloud.com/cover/788/920788/s_920788.jpg","title":"图说价值投资","author":"吴后宽","coverBoxInfo":{"blurhash":"KMSPCJx^*J.9V?f#XltRVY","colors":[{"key":"1/4","hex":"#360e1b"},{"key":"1/6","hex":"#3f021b"},{"key":"1/8","hex":"#47001c"},{"key":"2/4","hex":"#4d252b"},{"key":"2/6","hex":"#571c29"},{"key":"2/8","hex":"#620d26"},{"key":"3/4","hex":"#693a3c"},{"key":"3/6","hex":"#743336"},{"key":"3/8","hex":"#802831"},{"key":"3/12","hex":"#960029"},{"key":"4/6","hex":"#8f4d4d"},{"key":"4/10","hex":"#a63b41"},{"key":"4/4","hex":"#825453"},{"key":"5/10","hex":"#c45758"},{"key":"5/4","hex":"#9b6e6d"},{"key":"5/8","hex":"#b7605f"},{"key":"6/4","hex":"#b58986"},{"key":"6/6","hex":"#c4827f"},{"key":"6/8","hex":"#d17b79"},{"key":"6/12","hex":"#ec6a6b"},{"key":"7/8","hex":"#ee9591"},{"key":"7/10","hex":"#fc8e8a"},{"key":"7/12","hex":"#ff8483"},{"key":"8/4","hex":"#eabdba"},{"key":"8/6","hex":"#fbb7b2"},{"key":"8/12","hex":"#ff9b98"},{"key":"9/2","hex":"#f1dfdd"},{"key":"9/12","hex":"#ffb5b2"},{"key":"1/100","hex":"#d17b79"},{"key":"2/100","hex":"#ee9591"},{"key":"3/100","hex":"#ffffff"},{"key":"4/100","hex":"#F3E8E5"},{"key":"5/100","hex":"#F3E8E5"},{"key":"6/100","hex":"#270500"}],"dominate_color":{"hex":"#f27776","hsv":[0.7682239658586809,51.29330610893439,94.86794327023896]},"custom_cover":"https://weread-1258476243.file.myqcloud.com/bookalphacover/788/9